      <title>国际米兰老板正在与橡树资本、太平洋投资管理公司就贷款再融资进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/inter-milan-owner-in-talks-with-oaktree-pimco-to-refinance-loan</link>
